        <Param val="Hello&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Welcome to the PsychoPy script developed by Eli, for testing the human reaction time. I really appreciate your participation as every piece of data contributes to the final conclusion&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Press the space bar when you have finished reading" valType="str" updates="constant" name="text"/>
